query:
insert into underway.task_attempt (
                    task_id,
                    task_queue_name,
                    state,
                    attempt_number
                )
                values ($1, $2, $3, $4)
                on conflict (task_queue_name, task_id, attempt_number)
                do update
                set state = excluded.state,
                    error_message = null,
                    started_at = now(),
                    updated_at = now(),
                    completed_at = null
